system.file

Class FileItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • system.file.FileItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class FileItem
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is an Object Class which holds all the attribute of an imported model object file. The object consist of a ID, file name and the path. Other attributes are used to facilitate the GUI representation.
    Version:
    1.2
    Author:
    Andy Tsang
